    <item>
      <title>零售销售疲软显示消费者信心脆弱，美国国债收益率下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/treasury-yields-slide-as-weak-retail-sales-show-fragile-consumer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国零售销售数据疲软，增强了人们对美联储今年开始降息的预期，美国国债市场出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/treasury-yields-slide-as-weak-retail-sales-show-fragile-consumer</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 13:06:57 GMT</pubDate>
